00:12:20.230 --> 00:12:23.900
who had friends, you know,
who wasn't an icon frozen

00:12:23.900 --> 00:12:25.200
in time, was a real person.

00:12:25.200 --> 00:12:26.840
And really inspires us to think

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:30.500
about the power we could have
just being ourselves and thinking

00:12:30.500 --> 00:12:32.850
about you know, what we could do.

00:12:32.850 --> 00:12:37.610
And I think also it brings
people into the collection.

00:12:37.610 --> 00:12:41.010
So people read on their
favorite food blog, this thing,

00:12:41.010 --> 00:12:44.190
and I hope that inspires them to
think about what they could learn

00:12:44.190 --> 00:12:47.870 position:56%
about Rosa Parks from Rosa Parks
and brings them into the collection.

00:12:47.870 --> 00:12:53.840
The second goal we have at
NDI is to incubate, encourage

